Product.P_Desc: An enterprise-wide portal will enable space professionals to have rapid access to the information and services they need to accomplish their daily job
Product.P_Notes: this testing covers only the client application

Tester.T_scope: Covered in this testing is all pages in the client facing application:  Login Page, MySpace, About Us, Orbit Blog, News, Settings, Search Results, USSF Documentation, Sites & Applications, and the Landing Pages. Also included are the page loading state, and 400 and 500 error pages. This testing does not include pages that are outside of the scope of our team, such as the CAC authentication process, which is handled by an external service. It also does not cover the content management system (CMS) which is covered in a separate report.
